This project is based on the original work:

Python SEC Edgar
Author: Ryan S. McCoy
Repository: https://github.com/ryansmccoy/py-sec-edgar

The original project has been substantially modified, extended, and restructured.

Modifications include:
- Refdata normalization layer
- EDGAR index ingestion and parquet materialization
- Backfill pipeline architecture
- Filing-party extraction system
- CLI interface redesign
- Runtime compatibility improvements (pandas/numpy)
- Testing and documentation updates

